title: Kiss Person Person Medium Light Skin Tone Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a ropersontic kiss between two people with specific skin tones, symbolizing love and affection.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this kiss emoji featuring two people with medium-light and dark skin tones portrays a loving embrace, with their faces close together. The smooth, rounded forms and subtle 3D shading, characteristic of Apple's design, create a sense of warmth and connection. This emoji beautifully represents romantic love, intimacy, and partnership between individuals on Apple devices.
